   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ecobank Chad</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ecobank Chad (&quot;Ecobank&quot; or the &quot;Bank&quot;) is a leading bank in Chad with over 20% market share in terms of total assets and over 35,000 customers. The Bank offers its retail, SME and corporate customers tailor-made banking products and services. The proposed project will support the Banks lending activities by providing medium-term financing in local currency.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC&apos;s investment in Ecobank is expected to provide the Bank with medium-term financing in local currency to help it better support projects that require longer maturities than currently available in Chad, thus promoting development and economic growth.</narrative>
  </description>
